thread.title: Cheryl Keene
thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Cheryl Keene

author: Cheryl Keene
title: Cheryl Keene
text: We are very happy to have moved our camping trailer to Extra Space. Our previous storage facility allowed two major items to be stolen from the outside of the camper due to no gate and no cameras. At Extra Space, we can see the cameras and they have a new gate. The only problem we have is that there is no gate on one side of the building nor a keypad. Hopefully that will be fixed soon.
